Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:54.42,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs55}最近足球部真的很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.64,0:03:55.34,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\an8}是吧
